Package exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NoSuburbException
    The NoSuburbException is thrown when an attempt to determine a suburb with other location data failes
    NotExistingUserIDException
    The NotExistingUserIDException is thrown when the client tries to log in with ad user ID account that has not been registered yet
    UserNotConfirmedException
    The UserNotConfirmedException is thrown when the client tries to log in with an user account that has not been confirmed yet
    WrongConfirmationCodeException
    The WrongConfirmationCodeException is thrown when the client tries to confirm an account registration with a wrong confirmation code
    WrongDataException
    The WrongDataException is thrown when the client perform an operation on server giving wrong data
    WrongPasswordException
